Gold tried in the fire, or The burnt petitions revived. A preface. Walwyn, William, 1600-1681.
[4] p.
s.n.], [London : Printed in the yeere 1647.
Caption title. Signed at end: By a well-wisher to truth and perce [sic, i.e. William Walwyn. Cf. McMichael and Taft, The writings of William Walwyn, pp.275-6]. Publication date from colophon; place of publication from Wing. Signatures: A² . Annotation on Thomason copy: "June 14th 1647". Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
